&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Product Discoverability &amp;amp; Knowledge Architecture&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Modern Doc Migrations: Own the end-to-end migration and architectural overhaul of our user-facing documentation from legacy platforms&amp;nbsp; to modern, developer-friendly optimized documentation hubs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engineer Content for AI Agents: Architect and structure all technical documentation to be optimized for semantic search and Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), ensuring internal and external AI agents&amp;nbsp; pull flawless, highly accurate context.&lt;/li&gt;
